# Frontend Conventions

- Use `docs/code-conventions.md` as the canonical conventions document.
- Keep React component files under 300 lines.
- Separate concerns early:
  - extract reusable state/effects into hooks
  - extract helper logic into utils
  - split large visual sections into subcomponents
- Prefer readable, maintainable code over clever abstractions.
- Keep styling minimal unless design-specific changes are requested.
